                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2607.18703/2607.18703v1/x1.png",
                "caption": "Figure 1:AlayaRenderer-Flash restyling a liveSuperTuxKartsession in our\ninteractive web demo. The game engine continuously exports synchronized\nG-buffers to AlayaRenderer-Flash, which generates stylized RGB frames at\nplayback rate. Players can modify the visual style of the rendered game\nthrough arbitrary text prompts while the underlying gameplay logic remains\nunchanged.",
                "position": 291
